description: The video shows a simple animation. There are two items: an orange-red stylized apple and a green leaf. The leaf is above the apple. Beneath each object are thin, transparent blue ovals indicating that they are floating on water. Then two ducks pop up from under the water, one wearing the apple as a hat and the other wearing the leaf as a hat. They each wave their short stubby left arm and then their right arm. Then they dive back into the water, at which time several blue drops of water splash from the surface.
